{
  "stem": "5799.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And from Poland, we smuggled the border to Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We came to the Russian zone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the Russian zone, we smuggled the border again to come to the Americans, and we came and registered in the American camp-- UNRRA camp-- Schlachtensee in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'll tell you the truth that if not Truman, we would never come to the States.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You smuggled.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If I would be caught, I would be shot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You smuggled.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Russians would shoot you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Many were sent to Siberia and died there who were caught, some of our friends.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that's why I say, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was meant to be there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There must be something stronger, because not everything is because I took chances to survive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And from Berlin, we registered, and we waited a year and a half to come to the States.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And to this day, I resent-- I am a citizen here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I came here 48 years ago.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I am a citizen 43 years, and I'm proud of it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I resent that people come here, ask for asylum, and they are let in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I had to be three weeks quarantined.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Nobody looked what kind of a psychological-- not on me, but on the others, because women were separated from men in Bremerhaven, which, when we were going out from, from to the States, and given showers.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "People from the concentration camps thought they were being gassed, and they were screaming.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they couldn't talk any-- speak any English.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Nobody could ask for an asylum.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we knew that when we come to this country, we have to learn English.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't care how you spoke-- broken, not broken, with an accent, without an accent-- and this country doesn't owe you a thing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It let you in.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
